room_title: Escape room "Mission 51 Underground" by Clue Quest in Oklahoma City
room_description: As part of a covert operations team you have been given a mission to investigate the disappearance of two technicians at a Top Secret Research Facility. The details are very sketchy but you know you’ll be entering an abandoned mine shaft near Area 51. You will have 60 minutes to complete your mission before a self-destruct triggered by your entry will seal the mine shaft and its mysterious contents forever. Find the intel and get out — fast!!
